Package: mcpredomics
Title: Interpretable Multiclass Classification of Metagenomic Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Fabien", "KAMBU", email = "juniorkambu9@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-8233-6529"))
Description: This package extends the 'predomics' framework to support interpretable 
    multiclass classification of metagenomic data. It introduces One-vs-All (OvA) and 
    One-vs-One (OvO) strategies, multiple aggregation methods, and supports visualization 
    and evaluation of models. The package is especially suited for microbiome data where 
    accuracy and interpretability are both critical.
